Bem orgulhosos.

212
00:28:25,698 --> 00:28:27,125
Em breve?

213
00:28:28,384 --> 00:28:29,794
Sim.

214
00:28:31,454 --> 00:28:33,994
Em breve. Logo, logo, querida.

215
00:28:39,134 --> 00:28:40,704
Agora.

216
00:29:55,004 --> 00:29:56,644
Você mentiu pra nós.

217
00:30:01,744 --> 00:30:03,154
Menti.

218
00:30:05,554 --> 00:30:07,554
