237
00:33:56,144 --> 00:33:58,544
- Daryl!
- Oi.

238
00:33:59,384 --> 00:34:00,784
Papai!

239
00:34:01,664 --> 00:34:03,064
Oi, amigão.

240
00:34:06,884 --> 00:34:08,424
A Judith está lá dentro?

241
00:34:16,293 --> 00:34:17,703
Judith?

242
00:34:52,436 --> 00:34:53,836
Vem cá.

243
00:35:16,748 --> 00:35:18,148
Alfa.

244
00:35:23,648 --> 00:35:25,507
O que você estava
procurando?

245
00:35:26,489 --> 00:35:27,889
Eu achei.

246
00:35:50,178 --> 00:35:51,814
É lindo.

247
00:35:54,418 --> 00:35:55,818
Puro.

248
00:35:56,748 --> 00:36:00,657
Só vejo um saco de ossos
e dentes feios.

249
00:36:01,718 --> 00:36:03,188
Você verá.

250
00:36:04,058 --> 00:36:05,628
Talvez em breve.

